When making a personal finance decision, ask yourself the following:

How will this help me get closer to my ideal life?
What is the range of outcomes here? What's the best case and worst case scenario?
At what point will I change course? What would have to happen for me to change from this decision down the road?
What are my other options?
Who could this impact, and what do they think about the decision?


