Named for the debate tactic created by creationist shill Duane Gish, a Gish
Gallop involves spewing so much bullshit in such a short span on that your
opponent can't address let alone counter all of it. To make matters worse a Gish
Gallop will often have one or more 'talking points' that has a tiny core of
truth to it, making the person rebutting it spend even more time debunking it in
order to explain that, yes, it's not totally false but the Galloper is
distorting/misusing/misstating the actual situation.
 -- http://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=Gish+Gallop 


