 -- BAO


Many of you know what happens when the size of your Perl process exceeds
the size of your physical memory - you start thrashing. Well, that's
basically what happened to me. I couldn't get enough of the problem into
my head at once to make good progress, and I'm not actually very good at
subdividing problems. My forte is synthesis, not analysis. 
 -- Larry Wall


