* Regarding communication, who am I incomplete with?
* Regarding communications, in what ways am I incomplete?
* What is my payoff for being incomplete?
* What is the cost of being incomplete?
* From whom have I withheld communication?
* What statement, if it is delivered will make this communication complete?
* What do I fear will happen if I say it?
* Will I survive if I complete the communication?


