"_Feel_ the pain; _own_ it, make it yours - that which you own, 
you control; _forgive_ the person that caused it - not because 
it's OK to cause you pain, your forgiveness is not an OK signal 
to them - you forgive them so that *you* can go on with your life; 
and, last of all, _dismiss_ it.

The key here is this: you have two choices in regard to pain -
you can deal with it, or you can hold on to it. No third option
exists."
 -- Me, in e-mail


