10 principles of craft:
 -- --------------------
1) Act From Principle
2) Begin Where You Are
3) Define your aim simply, clearly & briefly
4) Establish the possible, move gradually toward the impossible
5) Honor necessity
6) Honor sufficiency
7) Offer no violence
8) Suffer cheerfully
9) Take your work seriously but not solemnly
10) Without commitment, all the rules change


